# Next.js & React Conventions

## App Router

- Dùng App Router (thư mục `app/[locale]/`)
- i18n qua `next-intl` với `[locale]` segment
- Server Components mặc định, Client Components khi cần interactivity

## Auth

### Token Management (in-memory, không localStorage)

Access token được lưu **in-memory** (module singleton) qua `token-manager.ts` — an toàn trước XSS.

```typescript
// src/lib/token-manager.ts
getToken()          // Đọc in-memory token
setToken(token)     // Lưu in-memory token
clearToken()        // Xoá in-memory token
tryRefreshToken()   // Gọi POST /auth/refresh (dùng HttpOnly refresh_token cookie tự gửi)
syncTokenToCookie() // Đồng bộ lên HttpOnly cookie (cho SSR) qua POST /api/auth/set-session
```

**Không dùng localStorage cho access_token** (rủi ro XSS).

### AuthProvider pattern

```typescript
// src/providers/AuthProvider.tsx
export function AuthProvider({ children, baseUrl }) {
  // state: user, loading (in-memory, không localStorage)
  // methods:
  //   login()    → POST /auth/login → setToken() in-memory + syncTokenToCookie()
  //   register() → POST /auth/register
  //   logout()   → POST /auth/logout → clearToken() + clear SSR cookie
  //   refreshSession() → restore in-memory từ SSR cookie (page reload) + verify /auth/sessions
}

export function useAuth() {
  // Trả về { user, loading, login, register, logout, refreshSession }
}
```

### SSR Cookie-based Session (Route Handlers)

3 Route Handlers quản lý session cookie trên domain puchi.io.vn (cho Server Components, Server Actions, Proxy):

| Route | Method | Mô tả |
|-------|--------|-------|
| `/api/auth/set-session` | POST | Set HttpOnly `access_token` cookie + `session_active` cookie |
| `/api/auth/restore-session` | GET | Đọc `access_token` từ cookie → trả về client (restore in-memory sau reload) |
| `/api/auth/clear-session` | POST | Clear cả 2 cookie |

### Client-side fetch

```typescript
// src/lib/fetch-with-auth.ts
fetchWithAuth<T>(url, options)  // Tự gắn Authorization: Bearer từ in-memory

// src/lib/client-api.ts
clientFetch<T>(path, options)   // Dùng fetchWithAuth bên trong

// Flow:
// 1. Đọc token từ in-memory (getToken())
// 2. Gắn Authorization: Bearer <token>
// 3. Nếu 401 → tự động gọi /auth/refresh (cookie tự gửi) → retry
```

### Proxy (middleware.ts)

```typescript
// src/proxy.ts
// Kiểm tra session_active cookie (domain puchi.io.vn) — không phải refresh_token
// (refresh_token cookie ở domain api.puchi.io.vn, JS/cookie không đọc được)
// Không có cookie → redirect /auth/sign-in
```

### API Contracts

```typescript
// src/lib/api-contracts.ts
APILogin: { url: '/api/auth/login', method: 'POST', data: { email, password }, result: { access_token, expires_in, user } }
APIRegister: { url: '/api/auth/register', method: 'POST', data: { email, password }, result: { user_id, email } }
```

### Key Files

| File | Vai trò |
|------|---------|
| `src/lib/token-manager.ts` | Quản lý in-memory token + auto-refresh |
| `src/lib/fetch-with-auth.ts` | fetch wrapper: Bearer + 401 interceptor |
| `src/lib/client-api.ts` | Client-side fetch (useAuth-optional) |
| `src/providers/AuthProvider.tsx` | Auth context + login/register/logout |
| `src/proxy.ts` | Middleware: check session_active cookie |
| `src/actions/auth.ts` | Server Action: logout (clear cookie) |
| `src/app/api/auth/set-session/route.ts` | Set SSR cookies |
| `src/app/api/auth/restore-session/route.ts` | Restore in-memory token |
| `src/app/api/auth/clear-session/route.ts` | Clear SSR cookies |

## Components

- **Shadcn UI** components trong `components/ui/`
- Feature components trong `components/<feature>/`
- Composition over inheritance

## State Management

- **Zustand** cho global state
- React Context cho auth + theme/locale
- Server State: React Server Components + fetch trực tiếp

## API Calls

- Client auth → `AuthProvider.login()` (gọi `${baseUrl}/auth/login` với `credentials: include`)
- Client backend → `fetchWithAuth()` hoặc `clientFetch()` — tự động `Authorization: Bearer` từ in-memory token + auto-refresh khi 401
- Server → `backendFetch()` với access_token từ HttpOnly cookie (set bởi `/api/auth/set-session`)
- API base URL: `process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` (https://api.puchi.io.vn)

## i18n

- Dùng `next-intl` với `useTranslations()`
- File messages trong `messages/`
- Không hardcode text trong component
